                            .layoutInfo__cont
                                .aboutUs
                                    h3.mb15 About us
                                    .aboutUs__cont
                                        img(src='images/aboutUs-img.jpg')
                                        p.text14.mb15 Bring more travelers from all over the world to get closer to the ASEAN is our biggest dream and especially Cambodia country with different cultures waiting for your discovery, we have now created a website named as cambodiaangkora to support our beloved clients Camdobia Airlines' tickets from international to domestic flights, hotels, tours, transports and airport pick-up. This website is another son of AN group, a travel company was founded since 2019.
